\c 21
\s UDavida ubala abantu
\p
\v 1 USathane wasesukuma emelana loIsrayeli\x + Jobe 1.6-9,12. 2.1-4,6,7. Zek. 3.1,2. Mat. 4.10. Luka 10.18. 1 Kor. 7.5. 2 Sam. 24.1-25.\x*, wavusa uDavida ukuthi abale uIsrayeli\x + 1 Kho. 21.25. Jobe 2.3.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho uDavida wathi kuJowabi lakubabusi babantu: Hambani libale uIsrayeli kusukela eBherishebha kuze kufike koDani, lilethe kimi ukuze ngazi inani labo.
\v 3 UJowabi wasesithi: IN\nd kosi\nd* kayandise ebantwini bayo njengoba benjalo ngokulikhulu. Nkosi yami, nkosi, abasizo bonke yini izinceku zenkosi yami? Inkosi yami ikufunelani lokhu? Izakuba licala ngani kuIsrayeli\x + Levi 6.7.\x*?
\v 4 Kodwa ilizwi lenkosi laba lamandla phezu kukaJowabi. Ngakho uJowabi waphuma, wahambahamba phakathi kukaIsrayeli wonke; wafika eJerusalema.
\p
\v 5 UJowabi wasenika uDavida inani lokubalwa kwabantu. Njalo wonke uIsrayeli wayengamadoda azinkulungwane ezizinkulungwane lezinkulungwane ezilikhulu ahwatsha inkemba\x + 2 Sam. 24.9.\x*; loJuda wayengamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane lamatshumi ayisikhombisa ahwatsha inkemba\x + 2 Sam. 24.9.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa uLevi loBhenjamini kababalanga phakathi kwabo, ngoba ilizwi lenkosi lalinengeka kuJowabi\x + 27.24.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo kwaba kubi emehlweni kaNkulunkulu mayelana lalindaba; ngakho wamtshaya uIsrayeli.
\v 8 UDavida wasesithi kuNkulunkulu: Ngonile kakhulu ngoba ngenze linto. Kodwa khathesi, ake wedlulise ububi benceku yakho, ngoba ngenze ngobuthutha obukhulu.
\p
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuGadi umboni kaDavida isithi:
\v 10 Hamba ukhulume kuDavida uthi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Mina ngikubekela okuthathu; zikhethele okunye kukho engizakwenza kuwe.
\v 11 UGadi wasefika kuDavida wathi kuye: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Zikhethele:
\v 12 Kumbe iminyaka emithathu yendlala; loba inyanga ezintathu uqedwa ebusweni bezitha zakho lenkemba yezitha zakho i\add ku\add*fice; kumbe insuku ezintathu inkemba yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ngitsho umatshayabhuqe wesifo, elizweni, lengilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* ichitha kuwo wonke umngcele wakoIsrayeli. Ngakho-ke bona ukuthi yimpendulo bani engizayibuyisela kongithumileyo\x + 2 Sam. 24.13.\x*.
\v 13 UDavida wasesithi kuGadi: Ngicindezelwe kakhulu; ake ngiwele esandleni seN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba izisa zayo zinengi kakhulu; kodwa kangingaweli esandleni somuntu.
\p
\v 14 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yathuma umatshayabhuqe wesifo koIsrayeli; kwasekusiwa abantu abazinkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisikhombisa.
\v 15 UNkulunkulu wasethuma ingilosi eJerusalema ukuyibhubhisa; njalo isayibhubhisa, iN\nd kosi\nd* yabona yazisola ngalobobubi, yasisithi kuyo ingilosi ebhubhisayo: Kwanele, khathesi buyisa isandla sakho. Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yayimi-ke ebaleni lokubhulela likaOrinani umJebusi.
\v 16 UDavida wasephakamisa amehlo akhe, wabona ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* imi phakathi komhlaba lamazulu lenkemba yayo ehwatshiweyo esandleni sayo iyelulele phezu kweJerusalema. UDavida labadala begqoke-ke amasaka bathi mbo ngobuso babo\x + 1 Kho. 20.31.\x*.
\v 17 UDavida wasesithi kuNkulunkulu: Kakusimi yini othe kababale abantu? Yebo yimi owonileyo owenze okubi sibili. Kodwa lezizimvu zenzeni? N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu wami, isandla sakho ake sibe phezu kwami laphezu kwendlu kababa, kodwa hatshi phezu kwabantu bakho ukuthi bahlutshwe.
\p
\v 18 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuGadi katshele uDavida ukuthi uDavida kenyuke a\add ye\add*kwakhela iN\nd kosi\nd* ilathi ebaleni lokubhulela likaOrinani umJebusi\x + 2 Lan. 3.1.\x*.
\v 19 UDavida wasesenyuka ngelizwi likaGadi alikhuluma ngebizo leN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 20 UOrinani enyemukula wabona ingilosi; lamadodana akhe amane ayelaye acatsha. UOrinani wayebhula-ke ingqoloyi.
\v 21 UDavida esefika kuOrinani, uOrinani wakhangela wambona uDavida, waphuma ebaleni lokubhulela, wakhothamela uDavida ngobuso emhlabathini.
\v 22 UDavida wasesithi kuOrinani: Nginika indawo yebala lokubhulela ukuze ngakhele iN\nd kosi\nd* ilathi kuyo; nginike yona ngemali egcweleyo, ukuze inhlupheko imiswe ebantwini.
\v 23 UOrinani wasesithi kuDavida: Zithathele, inkosi yami inkosi kayenze okuhle emehlweni ayo; khangela, ngiyanika inkabi zibe yiminikelo yokutshiswa, lezimbulo zibe zinkuni, lengqoloyi ibe ngumnikelo wokudla. Ngiyanika konke\x + 21.20.\x*.
\v 24 Kodwa inkosi uDavida yathi kuOrinani: Hatshi, kodwa ngizathenga lokuthenga ngemali egcweleyo; ngoba kangiyikuthathela iN\nd kosi\nd* okwakho, loba nginikele iminikelo yokutshiswa ngaphandle kwentengo.
\v 25 UDavida wasemnika uOrinani ngaleyondawo \w amashekeli\w** angamakhulu ayisithupha egolide ngesisindo\x + 2 Sam. 24.24.\x*.
\v 26 UDavida waseyakhela khona iN\nd kosi\nd* ilathi, wanikela iminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yokuthula, wayibiza iN\nd kosi\nd*; yasimphendula ngomlilo ovela emazulwini phezu kwelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa\x + Levi 9.24.\x*.
\v 27 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasilaya ingilosi; yasibuyisela inkemba yayo esikhwameni sayo.
\s Ukukhethwa kwendawo yethempeli
\p
\v 28 Ngalesosikhathi uDavida esebonile ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* imphendule ebaleni lokubhulela likaOrinani umJebusi, wanikela khona imihlatshelo.
\v 29 Ngoba ithabhanekele leN\nd kosi\nd* uMozisi ayelenze enkangala lelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa ngalesosikhathi kwakusendaweni ephakemeyo eGibeyoni\x + 1 Kho. 3.4.\x*.
\v 30 Kodwa uDavida wayengelakho ukuhamba phambi kwalo ukudinga uNkulunkulu\x + 15.13. 10.14. 2 Lan. 19.3.\x*, ngoba wethuswa yinkemba yengilosi yeN\nd kosi\x + Esta 7.6. Dan. 8.17.\x*\nd*.
